---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const demoModel = "/3dss/sample/core_viewer_baseline.3dss.json";
---

<Layout title="3DSL">
  <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400">Three-Dimensional Structural Language</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight">
      3DSS を “読む” ための Viewer と、サンプルの Library
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-neutral-300">
      /viewer は既存のまま。ここは導線と一覧と説明を足すだけ。
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href={`/app/viewer?model=${encodeURIComponent(demoModel)}&back=${encodeURIComponent('/')}`}
        class="rounded-full bg-white px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950 hover:opacity-90"
      >
        おすすめデモを開く
      </a>

      <a
        href="/viewer"
        class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Viewer
      </a>

      <a
        href="/library"
        class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Library
      </a>

      <a
        href="/docs"
        class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-5 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Docs
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Viewer</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
        既存の /viewer をそのまま使う。model 切替は ?model= で。
      </p>
      <a class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm underline decoration-white/20 hover:decoration-white/60" href="/viewer">
        /viewer を開く →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Library</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
        public/3dss/sample をビルド時に走査して一覧化。
      </p>
      <a class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm underline decoration-white/20 hover:decoration-white/60" href="/library">
        /library →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Docs</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
        スキーマ・仕様・Viewer ドキュメントの入口。
      </p>
      <a class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm underline decoration-white/20 hover:decoration-white/60" href="/docs">
        /docs →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
